@abstract:
Recovery and rollback semantics for the contractiles project.
Declares how to undo every significant state change — policy reverts,
deployment rollbacks, log replays, and event transformations.
@end

@requires:
- section: Audit
- section: Logs
- section: Policy
- section: Gateway
- section: Schema
- section: Dust-Events
@end

## Audit

### archive-audit-logs
- description: Archive current audit logs before any recovery operation
- handler: tar czf backups/audit-$(date +%Y%m%d%H%M%S).tar.gz logs/
- blast_radius: file
- idempotent: true
- preserves_audit: true
- notes: Always run this BEFORE any other dust action

## Logs

### gateway-decision-log
- path: logs/decisions.json
- description: Replay decision log in reverse to undo gateway decisions
- handler: dust-replay --reverse logs/decisions.json
- blast_radius: service
- idempotent: true
- preserves_audit: true
- verify_after: just validate-policy

## Policy

### policy-rollback
- path: policy/policy.ncl
- description: Revert policy to the previous known-good revision
- rollback: git checkout HEAD~1 -- policy/policy.ncl
- blast_radius: file
- precondition: git diff --quiet policy/policy.ncl || echo "Warning: uncommitted changes"
- verify_after: trust verify policy-hash
- notes: Rollback policy to the last known-good revision

### policy-config-rollback
- path: config/policy.yaml
- description: Revert policy YAML config to previous revision
- rollback: git checkout HEAD~1 -- config/policy.yaml
- blast_radius: file
- verify_after: just validate-policy

## Gateway

### bad-deployment
- event: deploy.failure
- description: Undo a failed gateway deployment, preserving audit logs
- undo: gatewayctl rollback --last
- blast_radius: service
- idempotent: true
- preserves_audit: true
- notes: Rollback to the previous deployment version; audit logs are retained

### bad-container-deploy
- event: container.failure
- description: Roll back to the previous container image
- undo: podman rollback gateway:latest
- blast_radius: service
- precondition: podman image exists gateway:previous

## Schema

### schema-rollback
- path: schema/schema.json
- description: Revert schema to previous version
- rollback: git checkout HEAD~1 -- schema/schema.json
- blast_radius: file
- verify_after: trust verify schema-signature

## Dust-Events

### decision-log-to-dust
- source: logs/decisions.json
- description: Transform decision logs into reversible dust events
- transform: dustify --input logs/decisions.json --output logs/dust-events.json
- notes: Produces a dust-events.json file that can be fed back to dust-replay
